{"view":"article","slug":"megaminx-westlund","category":"Megaminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Megaminx","title":{"en":"Megaminx Westlund Method五魔韦斯特隆德法"},"content":{"en":"<p><a id=\"_Hlk515277005\"></a><strong>Megaminx </strong><a id=\"_Hlk529730657\"></a><strong>Westlund Method五魔</strong><a id=\"_Hlk529730673\"></a><strong>韦斯特隆德法</strong></p><p><strong>Scramble method五魔打乱: (U* (R---- D++++)n)m</strong></p><p><strong>右手从最底面起手</strong></p><p>L*1=L, L*2=L2, L*3=L2', L*4=L'. F moves in Megaminx are more fingertrick-friendly and common than F in 3x3.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>F2L </strong>(First Two Layers)</p></td><td><p><strong>S2L </strong>(Second Two Layers)</p></td><td><p><strong>LL </strong>(Last Layer)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F2L / S2L\">F2L / S2L</span></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>White Star</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>White F2L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Yellow Star</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Yellow S2L</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Purple Star</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Purple S2L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Green Star</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Green S2L</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Red-Pink Edge</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Edge-Corner-Edge Block</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Do F' to Insert Block</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Red and Blue S2L</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>Solve Megaminx star like 3x3 cross. Move edge and corner of <a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> (S2L) pair into working layer directly above F2L (S2L) slot. Solve Megaminx F2L (S2L) like 3x3 F2L. The order of star and the corresponding S2L can be changed.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R U' R' U R U R'\">U' R U' R' U R U R'</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U' R U2' R' U2 R U' R'\">U' R U2' R' U2 R U' R'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>EO 翻棱</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_002.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image35.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_006.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image36.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_007.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image37.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F (R U R' U') F'\">F (R U R' U') F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F (U R U' R') F'\">F (U R U' R') F'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U2 (R2' F R F') U2' F'\">F R U2 (R2' F R F') U2' F'</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>CO 翻角</strong></p><p>Algorithm (the order of [] triggers can be arbitrary)</p><p><strong>z' [L*m<sub>i</sub> (R' U' R U)2]i [L*n<sub>j</sub> (U' R' U R)2]j </strong>(m,n=0,1,2,3,4, i,j=0,1,2,3)</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Do <strong>z'</strong> to make grey face on left back</p></td><td><p>Do <strong>L*m</strong> to make corner whose grey sticker faces forwards move to <strong>UFL</strong></p></td><td><p>Do <strong>L*n</strong> to make corner whose grey sticker faces upwards move to <strong>UFL</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Example CO</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_022.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image44.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>Scramble</p><p>(grey face on top)</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U2 R' U') (R U2 R' U2') (R U' R')\">(R U2 R' U') (R U2 R' U2') (R U' R')</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Solve</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"z' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (U' R' U R)2 L' (R' U' R U)2\">z' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (U' R' U R)2 L' (R' U' R U)2</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>EP 棱序</strong></p><p>Do <strong>U</strong> moves to solve two edges (except the last case), then execute algorithm below one or two times.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_024.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image45.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_026.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image46.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_028.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image47.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R2 U2' R2' U' R2 U2' R2'\">R2 U2' R2' U' R2 U2' R2'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' F' R U R' U'\">R U R' F' R U R' U'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R' F R2 U' R'\">R' F R2 U' R'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(L R U2) (L' U R') (L U' R U2) (L' U2 R')\">(L R U2) (L' U R') (L U' R U2) (L' U2 R')</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>CP 角序</strong></p><p>Algorithm</p><p><strong>z' [(U' R' U) L*m<sub>k</sub> (U' R U) L*n<sub>k</sub>] k </strong>(m,n=1,2,3,4, k=1,2,3)</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image49.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image51.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image53.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Do <strong>z'</strong> to make grey face on left</p></td><td><p>Do <strong>L*m</strong> to make the solved location of <strong>DFR</strong> corner moves to <strong>UFL</strong></p></td><td><p>Do <strong>L*n</strong> to make the solved location of <strong>UFR</strong> corner moves to <strong>UFL</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Example CP</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\Alienware\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\INetCache\\Content.Word\\Image_041.png\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image54.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>Scramble</p><p>(grey face on top)</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(R2 U2' R2' U') (R2 U R2' U')2 (R2 U2' R2')\">(R2 U2' R2' U') (R2 U R2' U')2 (R2 U2' R2')</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Solve</p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"z' (U' R' U) L' (U' R U) L2' (U' R' U) L'\">z' (U' R' U) L' (U' R U) L2' (U' R' U) L'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(U' R U) L2 (U' R' U) L2 (U' R U)\">(U' R U) L2 (U' R' U) L2 (U' R U)</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["F2L / S2L","U' R U' R' U R U R'","U' R U2' R' U2 R U' R'","F (R U R' U') F'","F (U R U' R') F'","F R U2 (R2' F R F') U2' F'","(R U2 R' U') (R U2 R' U2') (R U' R')","z' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (R' U' R U)2 L' (U' R' U R)2 L' (R' U' R U)2","R2 U2' R2' U' R2 U2' R2'","R U R' F' R U R' U'","R' F R2 U' R'","(L R U2) (L' U R') (L U' R U2) (L' U2 R')","(R2 U2' R2' U') (R2 U R2' U')2 (R2 U2' R2')","z' (U' R' U) L' (U' R U) L2' (U' R' U) L'","(U' R U) L2 (U' R' U) L2 (U' R U)"],"thumb":"/stats/alg/media/megaminx-westlund/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
